{"tid":2468743,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【義補】免費閱讀模擬試連批改（重開）","createTime":"2021-03-30T16:41:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T23:42:15.000Z","uid":69157,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6f19ee0adce769c98baaaa53c23d13a8fbeb7740","tid":2468743,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-30T16:41:14.000Z","msg":"【義補】免費閱讀模擬試連批改<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2353942\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2353942</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n舊po推唔郁再開過 更多詳情在舊post第一頁<br />\n<br />\n之前疫情無課室用<br />\n而家再來<br />\n可以一次過改埋文<br />\n時間日期：10/4 星期六下午3點半到6點<br />\n流程：<br />\n3點半到5點 P1開考<br />\n5點到6點 P1解卷<br />\n6點到7點半 P2 開考<br />\n<br />\n卷會兩日後寄返比你<br />\n<br />\n經濟有困難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嘅同學記得搵我<br />\n幫到一定幫<br />\n唔係就咁考咁簡單 我會各自比埋advice<br />\n位置有限 有需要就開多一日幫手<br />\n有改文嘅義工都可以聯絡我<br />\n<br />\n有興趣ig打我個名就搵到 profilepic黑色白字的"},{"pid":"7cc44f0f3eb0ada2f1cc6225d151886f7c8bc1fa","tid":2468743,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-30T17:25:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b3f1fa83e4776aaec9767e1a8fcabacb6849770","tid":2468743,"uid":369413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-30T18:18:00.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"717e0c7a8dc7f064a405c03d949f9e2d873597cb","tid":2468743,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-31T17:07:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"76e6411dca45a860cd17e33dca66d9640aee1500","tid":2468743,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T06:37:31.000Z","msg":"要點做先保到3 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />學校話我綜合勉強有個4<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><